oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Slave quarters
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: View of the slave quarters of Fairvue with overseer's house in the distance. The property is surronded with a wooden fence, with cattle in the background. Each house is made from bricks with a chimney. Another building [barn] is pictured towards the edge.
